  <div class="attachment-details">
    <h2 class="title"><a href="/government/publications/passenger-locator-form-privacy-notice/passenger-locator-form-privacy-notice">Passenger locator form privacy notice</a></h2>
    <p class="metadata">
        <span class="type">HTML</span>
    </p>


  </div>
</section>

</div>

  </section>



      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
    
          <div class="govspeak">
<p>Privacy notice for the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/provide-journey-contact-details-before-travel-uk" class="govuk-link">passenger locator form</a>. The notice explains:</p>

<ul>
  <li>why we collect your data</li>
  <li>how we protect your personal information</li>
  <li>who may have access to your data</li>
  <li>how long we keep will your data</li>
  <li>the legal basis for collecting and processing your data</li>
  <li>contacting you using your information</li>
  <li>how to make a complaint</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 4 November 2020
